{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, this approach has tremendous potential, especially in agrifood applications like precision agriculture and quality assessment of harvested produce.",
    "It allows precise identification and quantification of chemical compounds and other quality parameters in food samples.",
    "Initiatives like the NTIRE (New Trends in Image Restoration and Enhancement) spectral reconstruction challenges have catalyzed progress in developing these algorithms (Arad et al. 2020).",
    "However, fully integrating these algorithms is still an underexplored area in agriculture and food.",
    "Because consumer cameras are widely available and high-quality color images are easy to obtain at low cost, successfully applying these techniques could significantly expand the use of HSI."
  ]
}